('97824','33757','5','Villa for sale in 2nd line in Old Bendinat'),
('97825','33758','5','Old Bendinat is one of the most popular residential areas in the southwest of Mallorca. The precious Harbour Porto Portals, with its internacional restaurants, is just 5 minutes drive away. The villa was built in 2001 on an approximately 1000m² of land and 2006 restored by the present owner. Over the entrance on the ground floor you enter the spacious living-dining room with access to the pool and its terraces. Furthermore there is an office room, modern open kitchen, chidrens playroom, laundry room, utility room and guest toilet.\r\nAbout an oak staircase leads to the 1st floor with master bedroom with en suite bathroom, a 2nd bedroom with bathroom en suite, 3 guest bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. All bedrooms have access to a terrace with sea views. For the cars are 4 open parking spaces available. A separate guest apartment and a wine cellar complet the offer\r\n'),
